# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# File     : GRND035-dual-rule-remedy-chain-policy.ttl
# Domain   : Deontic Ontology / ODRL Grounding
# Problem  : Dual-rule: Power in remedy relator concerns founding event (B2)
# Refs     : Mohammed et al., What Does ODRL Mean? FOIS 2026
# Generated: 2026-03-26 by gen_foundation_problems.py
# Links    : Entailment/GRND035-dual-rule-remedy-chain-1.p
#            Entailment/GRND035-dual-rule-remedy-chain-1.smt2
